about.description:
HPP (Humanoid Path Planner) is a collection of software packages implementing
path planning functionalities for a humanoid robot. The core functionalities are well
suited to solve classical path planning problems. It can be extended to path planning
for other types of robots like digital actors for instance.
about.summary: hpp-gepetto-viewer subpackage of Humanoid Path Planner suite

raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "hpp-gepetto-viewer" %}
{% set major = "4.10" %}
{% set version = "4.11.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/humanoid-path-planner/hpp-gepetto-viewer/releases/download/v{{ version }}/hpp-gepetto-viewer-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 2f083aa9a4485af7b6b305a9ba1924e7bace84ca821ae2aa730fa90a964933f1

build:
  number: 0
  skip: true  # [win]
  run_exports:
    - {{ pin_subpackage(name|lower, max_pin='x.x') }}

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - cmake
    - make
    - pkg-config
    - doxygen
    - {{ cdt('mesa-libgl-devel') }}      # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('mesa-dri-drivers') }}      # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libselinux-devel') }}      # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libxdamage-devel') }}      # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libx11-devel') }}          # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libxfixes') }}             # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libxxf86vm') }}            # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libxext') }}               # [linux]
    - python
  host:
    - hpp-util ={{ major }}
    - hpp-statistics ={{ major }}
    - hpp-pinocchio ={{ major }}
    - hpp-constraints ={{ major }}
    - hpp-core ={{ major }}
    - hpp-template-corba ={{ major }}
    - hpp-corbaserver ={{ major }}
    - hpp-manipulation ={{ major }}
    - hpp-manipulation-urdf ={{ major }}
    - hpp-manipulation-corba ={{ major }}
    - gepetto-viewer-corba
    - gepetto-viewer
    - boost-cpp
    - assimp
    - octomap
    - urdfdom
    - ffmpeg
    - qt
    - openscenegraph
    - openscenegraph-osgqt
    - python
  run:
    - numpy
    - python
    - boost-cpp

test:
  requires:
    - pkg-config
    - hpp-corbaserver ={{ major }}
  commands:
    - pkg-config --modversion {{ name }}

about:
  home: https://github.com/humanoid-path-planner/{{ name }}
  license: LGPL-3.0-or-later
  license_file: COPYING
  summary: {{ name }} subpackage of Humanoid Path Planner suite
  description: |
    HPP (Humanoid Path Planner) is a collection of software packages implementing
    path planning functionalities for a humanoid robot. The core functionalities are well
    suited to solve classical path planning problems. It can be extended to path planning
    for other types of robots like digital actors for instance.
  doc_url: https://gepettoweb.laas.fr/hpp/hpp-doc/doxygen-html/index.html
  dev_url: https://github.com/humanoid-path-planner/{{ name }}

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ymontmarin
